				<article id="post-38767" class="et_pb_post post-38767 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-parent-portal category-post"><h1>Coronavirus Communication Updated 04/18/2020</h1>

				<p class="post-meta"> by <a href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/author/jsiegel/" title="Posts by Janette Siegel" rel="author">Janette Siegel</a> | Mar 11, 2020 | <a href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/category/parent-portal/" rel="category tag">Parent Portal</a>, <a href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/category/post/" rel="category tag">Post</a></p>
					
					<div class="entry-content">
					<p>Click this post for a repository for all School Communications regarding COVID-19 from PCCS in chronological order. For additional information please contact the Administration.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Timeline of Communications:</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Update 04/18/2020 – <a href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Letterhead.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Extension of Remote Learning</a>
</li>
<li>Update 3/28/2020 – <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/E-Learning-and-Governor-Pritzkers-Orders-March-28-2020.pdf">E-Learning and Governor’s New Executive Order March 28, 2020 </a></span>
</li>
<li>Update 3/21/2020 – <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/March-21-2020-Update-on-School-Closure-and-Governor-Pritzkers-Orders.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">March 21 2020 Update on School Closure and Governor Pritzker’s Orders</a></span>
</li>
<li>Update 3/16/2020 –<span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ISBE-Guidance-to-Schools-on-Mandatory-Statewide-Closures-3.16.2020.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> ISBE – Guidance to Schools on Mandatory Statewide Closures 3.16.2020</a></span>
</li>
<li>Update 3/15/2020 – Click <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Prairie-Crossing-Closing-Update.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a> f</span>or School Closer Update</li>
<li>Update 3/13/2020 4 PM. – Click<span style="color: #0000ff;"> <a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/COVID19-03132020-Notice-of-School-Closure-2.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a></span> for Notice of School Closer</li>
<li>Update 3/13/2020 3 PM. – Click <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/COVID19-03132020-Update-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a></span> for Update on COVID19.</li>
<li>Update 3/12/2020 – Click <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/COVID19-Deep-Clean-No-School-03132020.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a></span> for No School No Student Attendance Day 3/13/2020 Deep Clean memo.</li>
<li>Update 3/11/2020 – Click <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ieyu0K5v_U_Y2UmhCmQmOUrN3bJV-1g_PPns59Pd-GM/edit?ts=5e6917eb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a></span> for updated information from the Administration.</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;">Update 3/10/2020 – Click <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Prairie-Crossing-Charter-School.-Mail-Important-Notice-From-The-Executive-Director.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a> </span>for details about Farm to Table changes to help support the prevention of COVID19.</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;">2/272020 – Click <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://prairiecrossingcharterschool.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Coronavirus-Communication.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a></span> for the initial communication from the Administration.</li>
</ul>
